1,移动端设备优先 响应式缩放自动匹配移动设备

	在每个项目加入此行: width=device-width  设备的宽度
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximu-scale=1,user-scale=1,user-scalable=no"/>
	
2,布局容器 class="container" 容器的定义
	<div class="container">

	</div>
3,栅格系统 最多有12列,如果再多会换行
		col-md-1  中等屏幕
		col-lg-1   超大屏幕
		col-sm-1   小屏幕   平板
		col-xs-1   超小屏幕 手机
		1,中共可以分12列
				<body>
					<div class="container">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-1">1</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">2</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">3</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">4</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">5</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">6</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">7</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">8</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">9</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">10</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">11</div>
						<div class="col-md-1">12</div>
					</div>
					</div>
				</body>
		2,平均分3块,每块4列
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-4">4</div>
					<div class="col-md-4">4</div>
					<div class="col-md-4">4</div>
				</div>
		3,不同屏幕自动排列 
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">1</div>
				</div>
				
		4,列偏移 col-md-offset-5
		
				<div class="col-md-5">5列</div>
				<div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-5">2列</div>
		5,列的嵌套
					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-5">
								<div class="col-sm-1">sm1</div>
								<div class="col-sm-1">sm1</div>
								<div class="col-sm-1">sm1</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-5">2列</div>
						</div>
					</div>
		6,列的排序
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-8 col-md-push-4">push 8 列</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 col-md-pull-8">pull 4 列</div>
			</div>
		
		